<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/90458872-bookworm"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1617391461i/90458872._UY100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/90458872-bookworm">BookWorm</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Remy deluded herself into thinking that Elise only killed Jack as an act of self-defense. Remy believed that Elise felt threatened and thought that Ja<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Remy deluded herself into thinking that Elise only killed Jack as an act of self-defense. Remy believed that Elise felt threatened and thought that Jack was her abusive father instead. And despite what Remy thought about the situation, she also felt responsible for Elise in a way. The guilt that Remy had kept inside of herself wouldn't allow her to feel very badly towards Elise.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
