        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3335973314" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7060236534031120394">For a young adult book this was super dark, obsessive and very addicting to read. <br/><br/>The relationship between Elise and Remy was so dependant on each other that it was obsessive. The need to control and be with each other 24/7 was just crazy. <br/><br/>This book was very well written, the character development throughout only got stronger and I loved the way it finished.<br/><br/>Definitely worth a read. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


