    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2893039533" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2893039533" />
    <a title="Jessica" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/28045830-jessica"><img alt="Jessica" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1392050063p2/28045830.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2893039533?book_show_action=true">Aug 01, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jessica" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jessica" href="/user/show/28045830-jessica">Jessica</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2893039533" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4014498471860208132">&quot;Love is truest, strongest when you need each other, when you can&apos;t live without each other. Anything less is ephemeral. Anything less risks heartbreak.&quot;<br/><br/>If ever there&apos;s been a quote to capture a skewed view of love, it is the one above, but it captures what it&apos;s like to be young, defeated and needy. Remy and Elise meet when Remy is at a low point, and Elise seems like her savior. The friendship the two develop is lovely and wild, but it turns into obsession.<br/><br/> <img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1564688663ra/27925133.gif' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/> If I could put this book in the hand</span>
  <span id="freeText4014498471860208132" style="display:none">"Love is truest, strongest when you need each other, when you can't live without each other. Anything less is ephemeral. Anything less risks heartbreak."<br><br>If ever there's been a quote to capture a skewed view of love, it is the one above, but it captures what it's like to be young, defeated and needy. Remy and Elise meet when Remy is at a low point, and Elise seems like her savior. The friendship the two develop is lovely and wild, but it turns into obsession.<br><br> <img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1564688663ra/27925133.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br> If I could put this book in the hands of any of my former students, I would. Friends don't control you, and they aren't going to manipulate you into spending all of your time with them. Friends help you grow - they do not suffocate you. Remember that.<br><br></span>
  <a data-text-id="4014498471860208132" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

